data.title: Music Of The African Diaspora
data.meta_description: DUXX - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides information on various blues, jazz and folk musicians from the 1920s-1980s. It lists recording sessions for artists such as Side Wheel Sally Duffie, Eddie Duchin, John Dudley, Herve Duerson, Bo Dud and others. For each entry, it provides recording dates, label numbers, titles and sometimes notes. The entries range from solo piano and vocal recordings to full big bands.
